---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Home" 
  description="Portfolio of Ibrahim Nassar, a Full-Stack Web Developer proficient in React, Angular, Node.js, and .NET Core."
>
  <div class="relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-[85vh] text-center pt-10">
    
    <!-- Background subtle glow -->
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-full max-w-3xl aspect-square bg-cyan-900/20 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none animate-pulse"></div>

    <!-- Badge -->
    <div class="animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 100ms;">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-slate-900/80 border border-cyan-900/50 text-cyan-400 text-sm font-medium mb-8 backdrop-blur-sm">
        <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
          <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-cyan-400 opacity-75"></span>
          <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-cyan-500"></span>
        </span>
        Available for new opportunities
      </span>
    </div>

    <!-- Heading -->
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter text-white mb-6 animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 200ms;">
      <span class="block text-slate-300 text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl mb-4 font-bold tracking-tight">Welcome, I'm</span>
      <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 via-blue-500 to-indigo-400 animate-gradient-x font-normal pb-2 inline-block" style="font-family: 'Grand Hotel', cursive;">Ibrahim Nassar</span>
    </h1>

    <!-- Subtitle -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-medium text-slate-400 mb-8 animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 300ms;">
      Back-End / Full-Stack Web Developer
    </h2>

    <!-- Description -->
    <p class="max-w-2xl text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-10 animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 400ms;">
      Self-driven Web Developer with a <strong class="text-slate-200">Full Stack Nanodegree from Udacity</strong>, passionate about mastering software fundamentals. Building scalable solutions with <strong class="text-slate-200">.NET Core, Node.js, Angular, and React</strong>.
    </p>

    <!-- CTAs -->
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 w-full sm:w-auto animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 500ms;">
      <a href="/contact" class="group relative inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-cyan-600 text-white rounded-xl font-semibold overflow-hidden transition-all hover:scale-105 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(8,_145,_178,_0.4)] hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(8,_145,_178,_0.6)]">
        <span class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500 to-blue-600 group-hover:from-cyan-400 group-hover:to-blue-500 transition-all duration-300"></span>
        <span class="relative flex items-center gap-2">
          Get in Touch
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" />
          </svg>
        </span>
      </a>
      <a href="/projects" class="group inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-slate-900/50 hover:bg-slate-800 text-white rounded-xl font-semibold backdrop-blur-md border border-slate-700/50 hover:border-slate-500 transition-all hover:scale-105">
        View Projects
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- About Me / Overview -->
    <div class="mt-24 pt-12 border-t border-slate-800/50 w-full max-w-4xl animate-fade-up text-left" style="animation-delay: 600ms;">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-500">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 1 1-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 0 1 7.5 0ZM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0 1 14.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0 1 12 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632Z" />
        </svg>
        About Me
      </h3>
      <div class="glass-card p-8 rounded-2xl text-slate-300 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>
          I am a passionate and self-driven Full-Stack Web Developer based in Alexandria, Egypt. My journey into software engineering is rooted in a deep curiosity for how systems work and a commitment to mastering core computer science fundamentals.
        </p>
        <p>
          Since graduating with an Advanced Full-Stack Web Development Nanodegree, I have specialized in building robust, scalable backend architectures and dynamic user interfaces. My professional experience spans developing highly complex .NET enterprise solutions like custom ERPs and network management tools, to engineering real-time applications using Node.js, WebSockets, and Angular.
        </p>
        <p>
          I thrive in environments that challenge me to solve hard problems, optimize performance, and write clean, maintainable code using principles like Domain-Driven Design and Clean Architecture.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>